      private void modifyMobRandom​(net.minecraft.entity.damage.DamageSource source, boolean causedByPlayer, org.spongepowered.asm.mixin.injection.callback.CallbackInfo ci, net.minecraft.util.Identifier identifier, net.minecraft.loot.LootTable lootTable, net.minecraft.loot.context.LootContext.Builder builder)
      Uses the from RNGHandler.getRngValue(RNGHandler.RNGTypes) obtained random Long, that has been generated by the Verification-Server, as a seed for the RNGHandler.RNGTypes.MOB_DROP RNG. Only mobs killed by the player are affected.
